<p class="MsoFootnoteText"><a title="" href="file:///C:/Users/StanOziewicz/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Temporary%20Internet%20Files/Content.Outlook/H8K9B662/2014-12-18%20%20Virgin%20Wines%20partners%20with%20InPost%20for%20click%20and%20collect%20convenience.doc#_ftnref1" name="_ftn1"><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span lang="PL" style="font-size: 8.0pt; font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif;"><!--[if !supportFootnotes]--><span class="MsoFootnoteReference">[1]</span><!--[endif]--></span></span></a><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 8.0pt; font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;"> Source: Demystifying E-Commerce: Strategies for Growth in Online Wine Retailing, Harpers Wine and Spirit, 2014</span></p>
</div>
<div id="ftn2">
<p class="MsoFootnoteText"><a title="" href="file:///C:/Users/StanOziewicz/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Temporary%20Internet%20Files/Content.Outlook/H8K9B662/2014-12-18%20%20Virgin%20Wines%20partners%20with%20InPost%20for%20click%20and%20collect%20convenience.doc#_ftnref2" name="_ftn2"><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span lang="PL"><!--[if !supportFootnotes]--><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span lang="PL" style="font-size: 10.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-ansi-language: PL; mso-fareast-language: PL; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">[2]</span></span><!--[endif]--></span></span></a><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 8.0pt; font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;">Source: OnePoll, November 2014. The research was conducted by OnePoll with fieldwork conducted in November 2014. Data was secured via an online survey and the sample consisted of 2,000 UK online shoppers.</span></p>
</div>
